To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private ShootingStar _shootingstar;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_shootingstar = ShootingStar(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_shootingstar.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "shootingstar", _shootingstar.Current.Value);
}
